          <p class="prog-card__desc">Small group online sessions that build the core mathematical fluency every pre-IB student needs &mdash; starting with indices and the laws of exponents, then algebraic expansion and factorisation, radicals and surds, and Pythagoras&rsquo; theorem. Your child learns to set out full, annotated working from day one &mdash; the &lsquo;state the rule, then apply it&rsquo; habit that A-Worthy&rsquo;s own solution manuals are built around, where every line carries a short &lsquo;Why:&rsquo; explaining the move. By the end of Year 3, the foundations for logarithms, trigonometry and calculus are firmly in place.</p>
