            <li>Pythagoras&rsquo; theorem and its applications</li>
            <li>Coordinate geometry (gradient, midpoint, equation of line)</li>
            <li>Trigonometry and its applications</li>
            <li>Introduction to calculus: differentiation from first principles</li>
